# Copy this file to `.dev.vars` and fill in your credentials.
# Wrangler auto-loads .dev.vars in local dev.
# These values are NEVER committed (gitignored as `.dev.vars`).
#
# Get these from: https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials
# 1. Create a new OAuth 2.0 Client ID (Web application)
# 2. Add authorized redirect URI: http://localhost:8787/auth/google/callback
# 3. Add authorized JavaScript origin: http://localhost:5173
# 4. Copy the Client ID and Client Secret here.

GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your-client-id.apps.googleusercontent.com
GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=your-client-secret
